title: WTF | Watch: This GoPro getting knocked into a rattlesnake den will give you nightmares for days
text:
We're really sorry in advance if this suddenly gives you an extremely intense phobia of snakes but it wouldn't be irrational because this video is the stuff of actual nightmares.
We don't know why Michael Delaney would go out and actually look for a situation like this. One can only assume he's a Freddy Krueger in training.
Via YouTube
